body:
Everyone is welcomed. My name is Teetree-O Pittman

I am a junior currently attending Elizabeth City State University in Elizabeth City, NC. I am from Rocky Mount, NC.

I love to be physically involved with my work, also enjoy trying to challenge myself with different activities.
I used to play football for my high school from 2008 -12. I didn't play while attending this college so far, but I still like to lift weights just to keep in shape.

Helping people, even if I know it wouldn't benefit me, is something I enjoy doing also.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
